{
  "stem": "14737.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Can you imagine, if someone-- people were weak very much-- if someone, somehow bent down, he was finished, he was not more alive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as time went by, what happened to me, I somehow [INAUDIBLE], and there was some hook, and I was holding myself near a hook on a Friday night, as I can remember this.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was in the March of-- in-- in February 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I survived this night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And  as the night went-- passed by more and more, it became more and more roomier, because many people fell-- Just fell.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--On the floor, and natural died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I still had the strength.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I-- in the morning, they let us out again, the German SS.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I see they started to make big-- a big hall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So all those who were dead, they put them in that hall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I have seen three or four of my friends whom I remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One was a dentist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I saw him [? dead ?] there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we stay there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't exactly how long, maybe for another week or so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And horrible to describe was inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They slaughtered a cow or something like this, and they give something to eat, but not too much.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was near a town where there was Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were speaking German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know exactly the town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At one point, they went and brought us near a station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Probably that station was there, not far.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know the name, because I never looked up, and I don't remember [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And whoever was alive, they put in vans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they gave, for each one, a bread to divide at five, whoever he wants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we were in open vans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had open vans, not cattle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had open vans.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
